SwissLipids API basic search function

swissLipidsGetChildren.Rd

`swissLipidsGetChildren` Performs a search for potential children

swissLipidsGetChildren(entity_id)

Arguments

entity_id

`character` Search term for which children entries shall be searched in SwissLipids

Examples


swissLipidsGetChildren("SLM:000000352")
